Eris..Goddess of discord and strife.....:::<br>
<br>
::Wearing a black leather corsette and a black tight leather skirt that stopped at her ankles. Kneehigh black leaher boots encased her legs. Her usually grim red lips set into a deep smirk as her dark eyes sparkled.....oh yes.....they sparkled with anticipation..Around her wrist was a golden cord attached to a black velvet bag that was just a bit bigger then a fist.::<br>
<br>
Well, well, well....a party....and I wasnt invited ::grinning she looked around her at all the guests, stopping at Zeus and Hera:: Mother..Father...:::she looked to Poseidon and winked at him:: My dear uncle...<br>
<br>
::She began to walk to the bride and groom:::<br>
I would of made it in time for the ceremony....But that didnt concern me....:::she slapped Peleus on his bottom once then winked at Thetis:: And you two thought something could be hid from lil ole me...<br>
How foolish. I would of bought a gift. But what are material possesions really. Nothing more then to add to your position and ego's...<br>
<br>
:::Her eyes went from Hera, to Athena, to Aphrodite::: How lovely...It's mommy dearest, the virgin, and the..::coughs:: Aphrodite...::she gave a hearty chuckle::: This day is turning out better and better by the moment...<br>
<br>
::Her tounge ran over her bottom lip as she smiled greatly::<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
