<br>
'That my friends is a wonderful woman over there.'<br>
<br>
::He pats their heads as he comes up on Peleus and Thetis. He offers the mares to Peleus. He shales Peleus' hand in a firm grip but not so hard as to crush it::<br>
<br>
'For you Peleus. They are great steeds and are very swift. Not like the horses of this world but immortal.'<br>
<br>
::He hands to Thetis his envelope and hugs her and plants a kiss on her cheek.::<br>
<br>
'And this is a card wishing you, the married couple well and thanking you for you invitation to the wedding.'<br>
<br>
::The winds blows back Poseidon's curly ambrosial locks as he looks on the couple and smiles at them.:: <p>Poseidon~Lord of the Deep Blue Sea~Patron Of Horses And Sailors~</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#6A74B4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/unikeqofv.showPublicProfile?language=EN>NikeQofV</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Bronze Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 101<br> <font color=#FFFF00>(10/23/01 12:33 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2.topic&index=34>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.btinternet.com/~dave.newton/lysette-anthony/pictures/lysette-anthony109.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Patience</span><hr size=1> ::Pats Athena's shoulder hearing Eris's remark about not being invited:: Of course they forgot to invite the bad seed, its always easy to forget the prick of Olympus ::smiles and turns to Aphrodite:: Aphrodite, I have not seen you in so long ::hugs her:: I see your still working your stuff around the universe ::smiles and laughs. Walks over to Hera's side::<br>
